OL,3,CTax payers paid 'steep price' for Home
OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FThe cross-party committee said the
OL,7,FGovernment body ignored expert advice
OL,8,Favailable at the time during its bid
OL,9,Fto buy former HMP Northeye in efforts
OL,10,Fto secure 1,400 bed spaces, and
OL,11,Fbypassed processes to protect public
OL,12,Fmoney.
OL,14,FThe Home Office completed the sale in
OL,15,FSeptember 2023 under the previous
OL,16,Fgovernment, paying more than double
OL,17,Fwhat had been paid for the site 12
OL,18,Fmonths earlier.
