OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FNow the site, in Bexhill-on-Sea, East
OL,7,FSussex, remains in need of significant
OL,8,Fwork ` and the Home Office plans to
OL,9,Ftransfer it to another Government
OL,10,Fdepartment or sell it, the report
OL,11,Fadded.
OL,13,FIt also criticised the Home Office's
OL,14,F"dysfunctional culture" where value
OL,15,Ffor money was "a secondary concern",
OL,16,Fand branded it "unacceptable" to
OL,17,Frepeat the warning from its report
OL,18,Flast year.
