OL,3,CTax payers paid 'steep price' for Home
OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FThe report also cited the Northeye
OL,7,Fsale was among purchases of large
OL,8,Faccommodation sites for asylum seekers
OL,9,Fthat has gone "drastically wrong" and
OL,10,Fcome at a high cost to the taxpayer.
OL,12,FBibby Stockholm was one example
OL,13,Fdetailed after #34 million was spent
OL,14,Fon the barge which housed fewer
OL,15,Fmigrants than expected before its
OL,16,Fcontract ended in January, while #60
OL,17,Fmillion was spent on a site at RAF
OL,18,FScampton in Lincolnshire, which was
OL,19,Fscrapped by the new Government in a
OL,20,Fbid to cut costs before it opened.
OL,26,@qD@OOUqD@aO]
