OL,3,CTax payers paid 'steep price' for Home
OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FHe added: "The Home Office says it has
OL,7,Flearned the lessons from its
OL,8,Fdisastrously managed acquisition of
OL,9,Fthe Northeye site. These are lessons
OL,10,Ffor which the taxpayer has paid a
OL,11,Fsteep price."
OL,13,FThe findings come after a Whitehall
OL,14,Fspending watchdog, the National Audit
OL,15,FOffice, also said the Home Office's
OL,16,Fattempt to acquire the Northeye site
OL,17,Fin a few months led to cut corners and
OL,18,Fa "series of poor decisions".
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@MO]zD@COUzD@\O]
