OL,3,CTax payers paid 'steep price' for Home
OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FThe latest report on Wednesday said
OL,7,Fwhile the Home Office identified "over
OL,8,F1,000" lessons from its acquisitions
OL,9,Fof large asylum accommodation sites,
OL,10,Fcommittee members remain to be
OL,11,Fconvinced it can put learning into
OL,12,Fpractice.
OL,14,FThe report added: "Given that some of
OL,15,Fthese 'lessons' should have been
OL,16,Fevident at the time, we are concerned
OL,17,Fabout the Home Office's ability to put
OL,18,Fthat learning into practice and
OL,19,Fprevent such an unacceptable waste of
OL,20,Fpublic money from happening again."
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@FO]vD@SOU|D@cO]
