OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FMPs also flagged concerns that the
OL,7,FHome Office's bid to cut the reliance
OL,8,Fof hotels to house asylum seekers may
OL,9,Flead to increased costs elsewhere,
OL,10,Fsuch as increased homelessness and
OL,11,Fpressure on local councils by driving
OL,12,Fup rental prices.
OL,14,FBut the committee also praised work
OL,15,Ffrom the Home Office to boost
OL,16,Fengagement with local authorities and
OL,17,Fplans to work with the Ministry of
OL,18,FJustice on more funding to ease the
OL,19,Fgrowing number of asylum appeals.
