OL,6,FAmong the report's recommendations it
OL,7,Furged for the Home Office to set out
OL,8,Fto the committee how it intends to
OL,9,Freduce spending for asylum support,
OL,10,Fhow it will fairly integrate asylum
OL,11,Fseekers across local councils and by
OL,12,Fwhen the Border Security Command will
OL,13,Freduce the number of migrants arriving
OL,14,Fby boat across the English Channel.
