OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,FResponding to the committee's
OL,7,Ffindings, a Home Office spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We inherited an asylum system
OL,9,Fin chaos. The contents of this report
OL,10,Frelate to the previous government's
OL,11,Fpurchase of the Northeye site for
OL,12,Fasylum accommodation, but we have
OL,13,Fdecided against progressing the site
OL,14,Fto ensure value for money for the
OL,15,Ftaxpayer.
