OL,4,COffice asylum housing mistakes ` report
OL,6,F"As part of our overall effort to cut
OL,7,Fthe astronomical cost of asylum
OL,8,Faccommodation, including ending the
OL,9,Fuse of asylum hotels, we have surged
OL,10,Fthe number of returns, removing more
OL,11,Fthan 16,400 people with no right to be
OL,12,Fin the UK, restarted asylum
OL,13,Fprocessing, established the new Border
OL,14,FSecurity Command, and prioritised the
OL,15,Facquisition of more sustainable
OL,16,Fdispersal accommodation."
